(6569,'etc_blessed_scrl_of_ench_wp_a_i04','Blessed Scroll: Enchant Weapon (A-grade)','','When enchanted, P. Atk. + 4 for A-grade one-handed swords, one-handed blunts, daggers, spears, and other weapons. P. Atk. + 5 for two-handed swords, two-handed blunts, dualswords, and two-handed fist weapons. P. Atk. + 8 for bows. M. Atk. + 3 for all weapons. Starting at + 4, P. Atk. / M. Atk. bonus double. Enchanting is safe up to + 3. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.',1,1,1,'none','consume_type_stackable'),
(6570,'etc_blessed_scrl_of_ench_am_a_i04','Blessed Scroll: Enchant Armor (A-grade)','','P. Def. + 1 for A-grade armor and accessories. Starting from + 4, P. Def. + 3. Can be safely enchanted up to + 3. For one-piece armor, it can safely be enchanted up to + 4. HP gradually increases with each enchant level starting from + 4. If enchanting fails, the item will not be crystallized but the enchant value will be reset to 0.',1,1,1,'none','consume_type_stackable'),
